uth India, when it was probably a variation of a rich vegetarian curry. Our madras uses beef, and while this wouldn't be done in India where the cow is a sacred animal, it is a very popular combination in curry houses here."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 30m","6 portions"]}